---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Michael Zhang" description="关于 Michael Zhang">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <header class="mb-12 text-center">
      <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 overflow-hidden">
        <img src="/images/avatar.jpg" alt="Michael Zhang" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 mb-4">About me</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">技术探索者 · 终身学习者</p>
    </header>
    
    <!-- 去掉 dark:prose-invert，用 CSS 控制 -->
    <div class="prose prose-slate prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Hi, I'm Michael Zhang</h2>
      <p>一名热爱技术的开发者和创作者。</p>
      <p> I am an AI Infrastructure Architect with a passion for building reliable, scalable, and secure data platforms.

Over the past decade, I have focused on enterprise storage, networking, data protection, and modern infrastructure architectures. </p>
<p> My work has centered on helping organizations design systems that remain resilient, efficient, and ready for the next generation of AI workloads.

Today, my interests extend beyond individual products. I spend most of my time studying how storage, networking, compute, and software work together as a complete AI infrastructure stack.

This website is my Digital HQ—a place where I organize my research, share technical insights, publish podcast notes, and document what I learn along the way.</p>
      
      <h2>Focusing</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>博客 (Post)</strong>：分享技术文章、教程和最佳实践</li>
        <li><strong>播客 (Podcast)</strong>：录制技术讨论和行业分析节目</li>
        <li><strong>研究 (Research)</strong>：深入调研新技术和工具</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>What you'll find here</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 not-prose">
        {['AI Infrastructure', 'Enterprise Storage', 'Networking Technologies', 'Data Security & Cyber Resilience', 'System Architecture', 'Technical Research'].map((tech) => (
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">{tech}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <h2>Philosophy</h2>
        <p>Technology changes quickly. Principles last much longer.I believe the best engineers are not those who memorize products, but those who understand systems.This website is built around that philosophy.</p>
      
      <h2>联系我</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/michaelzhang-tech">@michaelzhang-tech</a></li>
        <li>Email: michael23leiz@gmail.com</li>
        <li>Linkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/in/lei-zhang-6257aa1a/</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>"Build knowledge. Share openly. Keep learning."</h4>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>